metadata.name: WE LOVE YOU
metadata.description:
Venice Beach has got it all: beauty of nature, celebration of art, freshness of the ocean, mixture of cultures, sense of freedom, struggle of homeless.

This series of photographs was taken back in 2014 during my first visit to Los Angeles.

These photos show all of the feelings that filled me while staying there.

Artist: Maria Nikiforova

Medium: Photography

Edition: 1/1

Year: 2014
